yle=&quot;font-size:9pt;&quot;&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;&quot;&gt;条件下：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma, verdana;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;SELECT article.aid,article.title,user.username FROM article CROSS JOIN user&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;得到的结果是被连接的两个数据表的乘积，即&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://baike.baidu.com/view/79382.htm&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#006EC6;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;笛卡尔积&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;&quot;&gt;实际上，在&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'DejaVu Serif\', serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;&quot;&gt;MySQL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;&quot;&gt;中（仅限于&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\'DejaVu Serif\', serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;&quot;&gt;MySQL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&l